Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.65,0:00:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:01:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Capturing the God Card"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mai's acting really weird up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hear someone calling me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who...?! Who are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is Mai seeing some kind of illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way you fools could understand what this woman is suffering from.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll make her suffer a terrifying loneliness beyond anything she's ever felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Executioner Makyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play a Magic Card\N with Executioner Makyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attach the Black Pendant to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card increases my Monster's Attack Power by 500 points...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now Malik's Monster has higher Attack Points...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's going to attack me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Dark Games are a world of illusions and phantasms...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And only those chosen can see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai Kujaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll let you enjoy the World of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Executioner Makyura attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazoness Archers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Trap Card keeps your enemy's Monsters from moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lowers its Attack Value by 500 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the Ally-Slaying Swordmistress counterattacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance of Betrayal!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who... was that just now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just vanished from my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I do wonder\N who he could have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But whoever it was that disappeared,\N I could care less either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved only the\N {\i1}darkness{\i0} since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Pendant's Effect states that when the Monster it is attached to is sent to the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the opposing player receives 500 points worth of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn has indeed come to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Executioner Makyura\N has a Special Ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can instantly activate a Trap Card from my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall activate this\N Trap Card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rope of Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card selects one of my Monsters destroyed this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It revives it with 800 extra Attack Points
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and allows it to attack again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Executioner Makyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swords of Judgment!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A befitting end for someone who betrays her allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure nailed a nice card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She contained the memories of one of your friends, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi's going to\N disappear from my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From within {\i1}me{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My parents died when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I lived alone\N in my deceased parents' house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ended up associating\N with terrible people...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter how much I wished for it, there was always something I couldn't achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was something I longed for ever since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then I met the Harpies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Harpies made themselves stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}by wearing armor and wielding weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lived in a similar way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I screamed this\N from the depths of my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But deep down, I lived alone and cried deep within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And eventually those guys appeared before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After meeting them...\N After meeting Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I slowly began to trust people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was no longer alone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had friends that believed in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now all of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is disappearing right in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... be lonely again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You won't be able to remember a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll wonder the dark in loneliness and descend into {\b0}true{\b1} darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now {\i1}disappear{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, just what the\N hell is happening to Mai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely... Malik is erasing the memory of Mai's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai! Can you hear me, Mai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai! You forgot {\i1}me{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once a Dark Game begins...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...you usually can't interfere with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But {\b0}I{\b1} can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yu...gi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! You {\b0}bastard{\b1}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't be confused by Malik's illusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Illusions?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I'm... just imaging this loneliness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a Dark Game, willpower is the key to success!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These illusions are created by the fear and terror in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Y-Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel... like I've lost something important to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something I cherished... deep within my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That voice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not sure who it belongs to,\N but it warms my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's {\b0}so{\b1} warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai, you have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you win this Dark Game, Malik's illusion will disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't ever let\N the light in your heart go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take back the memories you've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai, the rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep trying, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That voice again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's supporting me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's... important to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn that Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using his Millennium Puzzle to interfere with the Dark Game...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Has this woman\N regained all of her memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Either way, having the spirit to fight against me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My fighting spirit\N doesn't break that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking back what you've stolen from me in this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}if{\i0} you defeat me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you\N touch my memories again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play the Amazoness Chain Master in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I play a reverse card\N and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His Executioner Makyura has enough Attack Points to beat my Amazoness Chain Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He should attack right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unless he's afraid of my reverse card...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the Trap I've set\N isn't my {\b0}reverse card{\b1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the Amazoness Chain Master's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Amazoness Chain Master goes to the Graveyard while in Attack Mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}her "Brink of Death Chain Dance" ability is activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And by paying 1000 of my Life Points,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can steal one card\N from my opponent's deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you {\i1}over and over{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that loneliness is {\i1}not{\i0} an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's coming...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding Arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this to attack your Amazoness Chain Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}500 Attack Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he's {\b0}attacking me{\b1}\N with that Monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding Arms captured the Amazoness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why didn't it lose, since it has less Attack Points, big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Monster must have some sort of Special Ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing has the "Power of Invincibility" ability that renders it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unkillable against all opposing Monster's attacks for three turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding Arms doesn't hold enough Attack Points to defeat the Amazoness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more than enough\N to keep it from moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it'll be {\i1}slowly{\i0} tortured to death for three turns...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder just {\i1}how long{\i0} it'll take before it passes on~?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't panic, Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otherwise your heart will fall into Malik's Power of Darkness again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik! Stop this meaningless fight already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop this now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This {\i1}game{\i0}, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, the moment this woman loses to me in this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she shall fall into a deep {\i1}slumber{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is {\i1}not{\i0} "meaningless"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Torturing those little {\i1}friends{\i0} of yours...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lousy scum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very {\i1}nice{\i0}, Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hate{\i0} me! Say {\i1}more{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting to fight you for {\i1}1,000 years{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let your anger reach out\N and {\i1}touch{\i0} mine, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with this, Malik...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, this is {\i1}my{\i0} fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight him till the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean Mai will fall into a deep slumber?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... what a Dark Game is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark... Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! Burial Arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bury one Monster with this Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't {\i1}that{\i0} a shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Holding Arms is currently in Invincible State.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Effect won't {\i1}work{\i0} on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said anything about\N burying {\i1}your{\i0} Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazoness Chain Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since it wasn't beaten by {\i1}you{\i0}, my memory won't disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sending your own Monster to the grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the Amazoness Chain Master has a Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brink of Death Chain Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up 1000 points from my Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To take one Monster from your deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one I'm taking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is your God Card, the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rule, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine now!\N Your God Card, the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}really{\i0} think it'll go like you plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your suffering will be {\i1}legendary{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now {\i1}that{\i0} sounds fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that,\N you'll be dancing in {\i1}Hell{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You're awesome, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've been planning to steal Malik's God Card from his deck all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good job, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that you've taken his God Card, Malik should be considerably weaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But can you really {\b0}control{\b1} the God Card you've so effortlessly stolen from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So God has switched sides?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, now we can't tell who'll win this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik said only those connected to the Millennium Items can control God Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will God obey this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess we'll find the answer soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three sacrifices are required to Summon a god...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik has two Monsters on his field...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have anything on my field...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So all I have to do is evade my enemy's attacks until I get three Monsters on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the key to winning this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then... Let's see what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you Summon the god, you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't rush...\N Be careful, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Show me God, Mai Kujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set two reverse cards on my field!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as Amazoness Hands-On Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now just try and attack me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time {\b0}I've{\b1} got a trap waiting for {\b0}you{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik discarded his entire hand earlier, so when he draws a card, he'll only have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is your chance, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll attack Amazoness Hands-On Warrior with Executioner Makyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Makyura!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazoness Curse Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this Magic Effect, our Monsters will switch Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazoness Hands-On Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counterattack Makyura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pandora, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Executioner Makyura goes down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik only has a little remaining Life, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels {\i1}good{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when an enemy falls into your trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Card of Last Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Card of Last Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When one of your Monster's Attack Points is increased,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are permitted to draw from your deck until you hold five cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Malik used this timing to replenish his hand...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Executioner Makyura's Special Ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Makyura is destroyed,\N I can activate a Trap Card from my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I destroyed it thinking he didn't have a hand...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall let you taste\N even {\i1}greater{\i0} pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Torture Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll torture your Amazoness Hands-On Warrior to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Torture Wheel will strip away 500 of your Life Points every turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should {\i1}thank{\i0} you for trying to trap me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll match Trap with Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Trap, activate!\N Dramatic Rescue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card allows me to take one trapped Monster back to my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and play another Monster Card from my hand in its place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she going to use that card to...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to call the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra to the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I know the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra's Attack Points are based on the total Attack Points
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Monster used to Summon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if I called it out using that method, Ra's Attack Power would be zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty clever...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... there {\i1}is{\i0} a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to Summon the God Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Mai gonna get three sacrifices?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rescue Amazoness Hands-On Warrior from the Torture Wheel,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and return her to my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll play this Monster based on Dramatic Rescue's Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Lady Cyber Bondage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai's best trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please... let me Summon God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play the Magic Card Angel's Charity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card lets me draw three cards from my deck and discard two from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everything's all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me controlling God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, God is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The combo Mai is after!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:20:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God now obeys {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleidoscope!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Harpie Lady Sisters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then sacrifice my three Harpies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Summon the\N Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you think {\b0}you{\b1}, of all people, could control God?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That the god is\N already controlling {\b0}you{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winged Sun Dragon of Ra...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... isn't possible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(135,135)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge sphere hovers over the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really Ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then suddenly, the card set on Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}'s disk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,becomes covered with strange symbols...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who can read the text are able to control Ra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik begins to read the text...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Ra's control shifts to Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's changing form!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Secret of the Hieratic Text"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.14,0:23:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
